---
const today = new Date();
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<footer>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="footer-content">
			<div class="footer-brand">
				<h3>{SITE_TITLE}</h3>
				<p>당신의 아름다움을 위한 프리미엄 피부과</p>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-info">
				<p>
					<strong>주소:</strong> 서울특별시 강남구 (상세 주소 업데이트
					필요)
				</p>
				<p><strong>전화:</strong> 02-0000-0000</p>
				<p><strong>사업자등록번호:</strong> 000-00-00000</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="copyright">
			&copy; {today.getFullYear()}
			{SITE_TITLE}. All rights reserved.
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		padding: 4em 0 2em;
		background: var(--primary-dark);
		color: var(--white);
		margin-top: auto;
	}
	.footer-content {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 2em;
		margin-bottom: 2em;
	}
	.footer-brand h3 {
		color: var(--accent);
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
	.footer-brand p {
		color: var(--primary-light);
		margin: 0;
	}
	.footer-info p {
		margin: 0.5em 0;
		color: #ccc;
		font-size: 0.9em;
	}
	.copyright {
		text-align: center;
		padding-top: 2em;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		color: #888;
		font-size: 0.85em;
	}
	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.footer-content {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
		}
	}
</style>
